56:25.280 --> 56:26.998
Hey, jackass!

56:29.040 --> 56:30.393
Oh!

56:31.040 --> 56:33.998
Oh! Fuck you, man! What's going on?

56:38.360 --> 56:40.316
Fuck this shit.

56:41.280 --> 56:45.831
<i>- Bird! Bird, come back here!
- You fucking bastard!</i>

56:49.040 --> 56:50.996
