on a nice man like you.

01:02:49.040 --> 01:02:50.359
Oh, yeah?

01:03:01.680 --> 01:03:03.830
I don't think they're coming back.

01:03:41.600 --> 01:03:45.275
<i>Hi.
You've reached Robert, Nora, Emmet...</i>

01:04:08.400 --> 01:04:10.709
<i>They killed. They started to kill.</i>

01:04:10.840 --> 01:04:14.628
<i>Now, what's going to happen here
in a matter of few minutes is that...</i>

01:04:48.160 --> 01:04:51.789
<i>... being so bewildered with
many, many pressures on my brain,</i>

01:04:51.920 --> 01:04:55.879
<i>seeing all these people behave
so treasonous. It was too much for me.</i>

01:05:08.720 --> 01:05:11.188
You OK?

01:05:22.520 --> 01:05:23.748
