01:15:12.600 --> 01:15:14.192
All yours.

01:15:21.720 --> 01:15:23.676
<i>So what now?</i>

01:15:27.080 --> 01:15:28.433
I guess we do it.

01:15:34.000 --> 01:15:37.675
Um... I know we said
that we'd both take pills,

01:15:37.800 --> 01:15:41.998
